import React from "react";
import { Container, Typography, Box } from "@mui/material";

const TermsOfUse = () => {
  return (
    <Container style={{ maxWidth: "800px", padding: "40px 20px", backgroundColor: "#f9fafb", minHeight: "100vh" }}>
      <Typography
        variant="h4"
        style={{
          fontWeight: "bold",
          color: "#1a3c34",
          marginTop: "20px",
          marginBottom: "30px",
          textAlign: "center",
        }}
      >
        Landora Terms of Use
      </Typography>

      <Box style={{ marginBottom: "20px" }}>
        <Typography
          variant="h6"
          style={{ fontWeight: "600", color: "#2d3748", marginBottom: "10px" }}
        >
          1. Acceptance of Terms
        </Typography>
        <Typography
          paragraph
          style={{ color: "#4a5568", lineHeight: "1.8", fontSize: "16px" }}
        >
          By accessing or using Landora, a property management system designed to streamline property listings, transactions, and management, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Use. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you must not use our platform.
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      <Box style={{ marginBottom: "20px" }}>
        <Typography
          variant="h6"
          style={{ fontWeight: "600", color: "#2d3748", marginBottom: "10px" }}
        >
          2. User Responsibilities
        </Typography>
        <Typography
          paragraph
          style={{ color: "#4a5568", lineHeight: "1.8", fontSize: "16px" }}
        >
          As a user of Landora, you are responsible for ensuring the accuracy and legality of all property data, including but not limited to listings, descriptions, pricing, and availability. You agree to provide truthful information and update it promptly to reflect any changes. Misrepresentation of property details may result in account suspension or termination.
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      <Box style={{ marginBottom: "20px" }}>
        <Typography
          variant="h6"
          style={{ fontWeight: "600", color: "#2d3748", marginBottom: "10px" }}
        >
          3. Content Standards
        </Typography>
        <Typography
          paragraph
          style={{ color: "#4a5568", lineHeight: "1.8", fontSize: "16px" }}
        >
          Landora reserves the right to remove any property listings or user-generated content that violates our community standards, including but not limited to fraudulent listings, discriminatory content, or properties that do not comply with local, state, or federal regulations. Users must ensure their listings adhere to all applicable laws.
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      <Box style={{ marginBottom: "20px" }}>
        <Typography
          variant="h6"
          style={{ fontWeight: "600", color: "#2d3748", marginBottom: "10px" }}
        >
          4. Account Usage and Security
        </Typography>
        <Typography
          paragraph
          style={{ color: "#4a5568", lineHeight: "1.8", fontSize: "16px" }}
        >
          You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your Landora account credentials. Any activity conducted through your account is your responsibility. Notify Landora immediately if you suspect unauthorized access to your account. Landora is not liable for any losses arising from unauthorized use.
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      <Box style={{ marginBottom: "20px" }}>
        <Typography
          variant="h6"
          style={{ fontWeight: "600", color: "#2d3748", marginBottom: "10px" }}
        >
          5. Intellectual Property
        </Typography>
        <Typography
          paragraph
          style={{ color: "#4a5568", lineHeight: "1.8", fontSize: "16px" }}
        >
          All content, features, and functionality on the Landora platform, including logos, designs, and software, are the property of Landora or its licensors and are protected by intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from any part of the platform without prior written consent.
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      <Box style={{ marginBottom: "20px" }}>
        <Typography
          variant="h6"
          style={{ fontWeight: "600", color: "#2d3748", marginBottom: "10px" }}
        >
          6. Limitation of Liability
        </Typography>
        <Typography
          paragraph
          style={{ color: "#4a5568", lineHeight: "1.8", fontSize: "16px" }}
        >
          Landora provides its services on an "as-is" basis and is not liable for any damages arising from the use of the platform, including but not limited to errors in property listings, disputes between users, or interruptions in service. Users assume all risks associated with transactions conducted through Landora.
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      <Box style={{ marginBottom: "20px" }}>
        <Typography
          variant="h6"
          style={{ fontWeight: "600", color: "#2d3748", marginBottom: "10px" }}
        >
          7. Termination
        </Typography>
        <Typography
          paragraph
          style={{ color: "#4a5568", lineHeight: "1.8", fontSize: "16px" }}
        >
          Landora may suspend or terminate your access to the platform at any time, with or without notice, for violations of these Terms of Use or for any other reason deemed necessary to protect the platform or its users. Upon termination, your right to access Landora will cease immediately.
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      <Typography
        style={{
          color: "#718096",
          fontSize: "14px",
          textAlign: "center",
          marginTop: "40px",
          borderTop: "1px solid #e2e8f0",
          paddingTop: "20px",
        }}
      >
        Last updated: August 26, 2025
      </Typography>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default TermsOfUse;
